io.konik.zugferd.unece.codes

Enum DateTimeType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<DateTimeType>
      • io.konik.zugferd.unece.codes.DateTimeType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<DateTimeType>

    public enum DateTimeType
extends Enum<DateTimeType>

    The Date Time Types

    Enumeration contains some of the UNEC 2379 codes and formats. This Enumeration does not contain periods formats.

    See Also:
    UN/EDIFACT 2379 Date or time or period format code
